title: Secret Warriors, Vol. 6: Wheels Within Wheels
description: What ties Hydra, The Howling Commandos, and Leviathan together? How did Nick Fury, Dum Dum Dugan, Baron Von Strucker, Kraken, and Orion become part of the same mysterious organization? It's all here in Wheels within Wheels.Collecting: Secret Warriors 24-28
author: Jonathan Hickman
